{"tid":1857512,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【回應讀者「覺得」最近自殺報道比過往少】","createTime":"2020-02-02T08:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T06:40:05.000Z","uid":4273,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"58281549ab747ba96ed47ace259324ef23f297af","tid":1857512,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgpZDQZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgpZDQZ.jpg&h=9323a341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【回應讀者「覺得」最近自殺報道比過往少】<br />\n<br />\n根據資料庫記錄，截至 2020-02-01 00:30 ，2020年1月共錄得87人自殺，當中有59人自殺身亡，分別每天平均2.81人及1.9人。<br />\n<br />\n對比去年當月同期累積統計共錄得77人自殺，升幅約12.99%，對比去年當月同期累積每天平均2.48人，升幅約13.31%。<br />\n<br />\n對比上月統計共錄得76人自殺，升幅約14.47%，對比上月每天平均2.45人，升幅約14.69%。<br />\n<br />\n去年共錄得1042人自殺，當中有722人自殺身亡，分別每天平均2.85及1.98人。<br />\n<br />\n上月共錄得87人自殺，當中有59人自殺身亡，分別每天平均2.81及1.9人，對比上上月升幅約14.47%及完全相同，對比過往三個月平均升幅約25.48%及每天平均升幅約24.44%。<br />\n<br />\n※ 本文件旨在記錄香港每日由新聞報道之自殺資料，以便用作討論。 ※ 本文件並非鼓吹自殺行為，請珍惜生命，關心身邊家人及朋友。 ※<br />\n<br />\n/ / 統 計 分 析 從 來 只 會 反 映 整 體 的 客 觀 事 實 ， 並 不 會 成 為 任 何 論 述 的 助 燃 劑 。 除 了 實 質 證 據 能 告 訴 我 們 事 實 真 相 ， 其 他 數 字 都 只 能 作 為 一 般 參 考 。 / /<br />\n<br />\n【香港自殺報道資料庫】<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/HKSuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2FHKSuicide&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=4b22ad69\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/HKSuicide</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.com/siuyeongHKSuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FsiuyeongHKSuicide&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=ffb70ce3\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/siuyeongHKSuicide</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/siuyeongHKSuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FsiuyeongHKSuicide&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=b4294fcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/siuyeongHKSuicide</a><br />\n<br />\n【 2 0 1 9 年 】<br />\n簡單總結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3afIK3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3afIK3g&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=8a8fcdad\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3afIK3g</a><br />\n自殺率％：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/30fyAuE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30fyAuE&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=17e2e7f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/30fyAuE</a><br />\n開放數據：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2FJMxrr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FJMxrr&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=9f611231\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FJMxrr</a>"},{"pid":"7c94f22931cc37d2eb2a4b24a81af25ad7878f65","tid":1857512,"uid":39556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:27:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f0fbd4acedc368c4874320a8efd456ca65948238","tid":1857512,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd9c24b6a6a0582ab11a6b25204a2eb2c829afa","tid":1857512,"uid":64745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:30:25.000Z","msg":"pusj"},{"pid":"3ce93cfd1e72c404762a980812cc71ad81f16a3b","tid":1857512,"uid":120431,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324372ecfc2b4172d7f576a40e41d30d76863186","tid":1857512,"uid":64092,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"只係我地無留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa4da44561bcac47b271bce64d572a8a96de7b3","tid":1857512,"uid":4273,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"324372ecfc2b4172d7f576a40e41d30d76863186","tid":1857512,"uid":64092,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"只係我地無留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:46:17.000Z","msg":"對，肺炎報道量遠多過自殺報道量，造成錯覺～"},{"pid":"33e942d6463cad633c72af3f85a41a3984bcb220","tid":1857512,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a38825ce3d1bbd976dd29abe31fcebec53a75db","tid":1857512,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc38332a4e8776223f9ae44969c7599edf5254b","tid":1857512,"uid":21641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d1e69b7627f843d3b60087ee083b930d4a1f3c17","tid":1857512,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:27:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8770517d7e821878555dbdabdec2fb2c866a086","tid":1857512,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"趁大家注意力去晒留意武漢肺炎 黑警殺人更少顧慮"},{"pid":"e20f12565a4144900a9b0d64fb0c88ed3375200a","tid":1857512,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:53:35.000Z","msg":"即係冇少到?"},{"pid":"c3728c239b52338724e8b2dc8afc46ca7eb7c9d2","tid":1857512,"uid":4273,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e20f12565a4144900a9b0d64fb0c88ed3375200a","tid":1857512,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:53:35.000Z","msg":"即係冇少到?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:55:49.000Z","msg":"相反升少少"},{"pid":"232155eb69d3d657a9c97db87ce5ce7cbaed02be","tid":1857512,"uid":106851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dba5583ce1c8da18c937897c111c7833d06fe113","tid":1857512,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下你數據收集的方法?"},{"pid":"4b0248892e228c7019351241e7b737bff39a9461","tid":1857512,"uid":4273,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"dba5583ce1c8da18c937897c111c7833d06fe113","tid":1857512,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下你數據收集的方法?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"記錄主要從正式媒體發佈的自殺報道<br />\n<br />\n<ins>如何判斷該報道為自殺報道？</ins><br />\n於客觀的情況下，一般的報道內容並不會提及「防止自殺等求助途徑或訊息」，相反有提及到相關訊息的報道，會客觀判斷為自殺報道，亦有部份報道沒有提及到相關訊息但有提及相關字眼如自殺，遺書等，能令讀者客觀判斷為自殺報道，亦會被記錄到資料庫中。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>請問文件是有甚麼記錄準則？</ins><br />\n文件只會記錄正式的媒體發佈的自殺（或企圖自殺）新聞如東網、蘋果、香港０１、明報、經濟、星島、ＡＭ７３０&hellip;等等，然而沒有正式的媒體報道，作者並不會記錄於文件當中，尤其是流傳於 Ｆａｃｅｂｏｏｋ、Ｔｅｌｅｇｒａｍ、內容農場&hellip;等等。"},{"pid":"f924083985b8ea391693d02161c08526b5a625aa","tid":1857512,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b0248892e228c7019351241e7b737bff39a9461","tid":1857512,"uid":4273,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"dba5583ce1c8da18c937897c111c7833d06fe113","tid":1857512,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下你數據收集的方法?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"記錄主要從正式媒體發佈的自殺報道<br />\n<br />\n<ins>如何判斷該報道為自殺報道？</ins><br />\n於客觀的情況下，一般的報道內容並不會提及「防止自殺等求助途徑或訊息」，相反有提及到相關訊息的報道，會客觀判斷為自殺報道，亦有部份報道沒有提及到相關訊息但有提及相關字眼如自殺，遺書等，能令讀者客觀判斷為自殺報道，亦會被記錄到資料庫中。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>請問文件是有甚麼記錄準則？</ins><br />\n文件只會記錄正式的媒體發佈的自殺（或企圖自殺）新聞如東網、蘋果、香港０１、明報、經濟、星島、ＡＭ７３０&hellip;等等，然而沒有正式的媒體報道，作者並不會記錄於文件當中，尤其是流傳於 Ｆａｃｅｂｏｏｋ、Ｔｅｌｅｇｒａｍ、內容農場&hellip;等等。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"好奇一問，Ching 係用人手？爬蟲？拎上一兩年的數據？定個project係6月前已經開始？"},{"pid":"880dd3b0ddba252c2050a19d3eb84cb865b77167","tid":1857512,"uid":344033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:43:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家幫手推一推，正個評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">